<plot>As a tribe of Indians sings, the women are all falling for the three singers of the title, 'Bing Crosby' (qv), 'Russ Columbo' (qv), and 'Rudy Vallee' (qv). A brave brings a radio to his girlfriend, and she joins in the title song. The woodland animals join in, doing impersonations. While the tribe dances, a fire gets out of control. Three baby birds, trapped in a tree, are saved by a spider web used as a net.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?119333</url></doc>
